Punch:




Punch, once a double agent for the Alliance, was now just working the 
computers.  But that was ok, he was safe.  Sitting at the controls of the 
original Alliance base, he began a thorough scanners sweep of the entire 
island they were on.  With the recent attack and all, he had to be sure no 
one had snuck in.
